gcs - Git Commits Since

USAGE:
    gcs <sha1-hash|date|date-expression>

DESCRIPTION:
    List all SHA hashes of commits since the provided reference.

ARGUMENTS:
    sha1-hash|date|date-expression
        Reference point (SHA1 hash, date, or date expression)

EXAMPLES:
    gcs abc123
    gcs "2025/01/01"
    gcs "1 week ago"
    gcs "yesterday"
